{
  "chapter": 92,
  "chapter_summary": "赵穆因乐乘被刺杀而方寸大乱，清早来找项少龙（董匡）商议对策。项少龙佯装惊愕，暗中探听晶王后与赵穆的关系，得知二人只是互相利用。赵穆命他通过赵雅探听孝成王动向。善柔等人归来，与项少龙打情骂俏，田氏姊妹侍奉左右。赵致带回邯郸全城大搜的消息，荆俊汇报乌卓已送伤员回牧场休养。黄昏时平山侯韩闯来访，揭露自己乃晶王后族弟，主动提议帮项少龙谋取城守之位，条件是与赵穆、郭纵划清界限，并安排他面见晶王后。项少龙喜出望外，乐乘之死带来的政治变局远超预期。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷为何脸色变得比我还要难看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的伤势如何？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "其实只是皮肉伤，不过受了风寒，躺足一天一夜已好多哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乐乘昨晚出事了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨晚乐乘返回别府途中遇袭，头给人砍掉，二百多名亲卫非死即伤，唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "那个项少龙真的这么厉害？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事发时附近民居的人确听到有人自称项少龙，不过这批人全体裹头蒙脸，无人能看到真面目，事后搜捕的人发觉城东一批城兵亦被人干掉，只留下些攀城的长索，可是城墙外却不见足印。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "那么说项少龙仍应潜伏在城内，侯爷还不赶快挖他出来。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还用你教吗？现在整个邯郸城给翻转过来，除非项少龙和他的人变成会打洞的耗子，否则定要现形。可是直到此刻，连他的影子都看不到，你能告诉我是什么一回事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "谁会坐上城守之职？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "暂时该是成胥！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "此事相当不妙。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你明白哩！乐乘一死，最大的得益者是孝成王，对项少龙有什么好处？项少龙若要杀人，何时轮到乐乘？孝成王这一着确是心狠手辣，说不定是赵雅那贱人教他。项少龙若能来去自如，我和孝成王早没命了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "先下手为强，侯爷若可通过晶王后下毒，岂非可一举解决所有问题？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你当晶王后是我的手下吗？她才不会蠢得直接参与弒杀行动。但假若能杀死孝成王那昏君，我会有操纵她的方法，唉！你教我现在该怎么办？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有些事急也急不来，幸好我尚有你这支无人知道的奇兵，仍未算一败涂地，但少了乐乘，自是声势大弱，田单绝不会像以前般热心对待我了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先养好伤再说吧，我还要见见其他人，好安抚他们的心。你设法再由赵雅那处探听消息，看孝成王有什么动静。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷小心有人会变节，人心叵测，很难说哩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个本侯怎会不晓得，以后有事再找你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "最大那头老虎是谁打的呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "当然是另一头雌老虎，董某甘拜下风。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们只伤了十多人，真是奇闻罕事，说出来都没有人相信。不若索性把田单干掉，那时你要人家怎样从你都可以，像她两姊妹那样也行。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你的乖妹子到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要顾左右而言他！算什么好汉子？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "致夫人到外面去探听消息。哎哟！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这般霸道的女人，我老董还是首次见到，让我把驯野马的功夫搬来对付你！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你敢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "姊姊进步多了，只是动手而不出刀子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你还未够本领令本姑娘心动，回家多学几年功夫吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng",
      "speaker_name": "田凤",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "柔夫人其实心中爱煞了董爷，平时总爱和我们谈着你的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那你们呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董爷爱吃什么东西？奴家去弄来给你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_zhen",
      "text": "随便好了！嘿！那头雌老虎到哪里去了呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "田贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "老虎白天自然是躲在虎穴里睡觉！小凤在服侍她。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我从未见过邯郸城变成这个样子，街上处处均是赵兵，逐家逐户搜查问话，我们行馆的武士都被征召去帮手，弄得人心惶惶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "是否有人认为是我干的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董爷你最厉害是没有出动飞针，那已成为你的招牌，所以现下人人疑神疑鬼，我师父甚至怀疑是李园干的，嘿！真是好笑！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我从未见过致姊这么开心的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "真多事！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "大哥到哪去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大哥回牧场去了。趁赵人把注意力集中在民居时，送那些受伤的兄弟回牧场医治休息，免得被人发觉出破绽。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大哥本来想找三哥说话，但三哥……嘿！",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "小俊你为何吞吞吐吐，究竟你三哥怎样了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_feng",
      "speaker_name": "田凤",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董爷要不要尝尝龙阳君送来的补酒？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三哥最需要的就是这东西，你也过来陪我们喝两杯吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若非虚不受补，凡男人都需要这东西，来！把贞贞唤来，大家高兴一下。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄比马儿还强壮，脸色较昨天好多哩！伤口还痛吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "侯爷有心，今天确好了很多。唉！想不到乐乘将军就这么去了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这世上有些人假如忽然给人杀掉，事后定没有人可猜出是谁行凶的，因为被他害过的人实在太多了。若有机会，我也会砍他两剑。昔日乐乘驻守赵、韩边疆，便曾多次侵入我境犯事，两手染满血腥，哼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "原来乐将军是这样的一个人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要再提这个人了，让我们商量一下将来的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄今天回赵，不外是希望有一番建树。但养马终是养马，顶多变成第二个乌氏倮，与官爵无望，董兄认为我这番话对吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "侯爷看得起鄙人，自是不胜感激，只不过……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄误会了，当然哩！若董兄要来敝国，本侯定必倒屣相迎，但今天要商量的，却是邯郸城守因乐乘之死腾出来的空缺。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄想不到吧！但若知晶王后乃本侯族姊，便知我对赵国朝政并非没有影响力。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "这个鄙人倒不知道哩！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要我在晶王后跟前说上两句，包保她可影响孝成王的决定。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "孝成王不是挑选成胥代乐乘吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "成胥是什么东西，硬将项少龙的功劳分一半过去，才混至今天的位置，声望、能力均不足以服众，现下是士急马行田，暂时性的措施吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "鄙人来到邯郸日子尚短，屁股尚未坐暖，连排列队末的资格都欠缺，韩侯不用费心了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄太小觑自己，目前的你已是邯郸臣民中家喻户晓的人，声势如日中天，从千头战马的大礼，以至力挫楚人、硬闯城门、勇救龙阳君，若以你为城守，谁不认为最是称职。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "只是硬闯城门一项，休想大王肯点头。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "黑可以说成白，白可说成黑，靠的仍是一张嘴巴。若孝成王起用你，正可表示出他的豁达大度，用人唯才。董兄是万事俱备，欠的只是说话的那张嘴巴。我更可以设法影响赵雅，有她两人为你说项，何愁大事不成？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "这番恩德，董某应怎样报答侯爷？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大家自己人，还要说这种话吗？来！我先安排你见晶王后一面，其他迟些再说。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "记紧绝不要和赵穆或郭纵牵上任何关系，同时不要开罪赵雅或郭开，那样城守之位，八成会落在你身上。嘿！孝成王对你救回龙阳君一事，确是非常欣赏！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "龙阳君好了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若你要躺上一天，那他最少要躺十天才行，噢！那对孪生姊妹花如何？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "韩侯要她们陪你还不容易，不过最好尽量不让人怀疑我们间的关系，到我真个当上城守，便不用惧怕了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄说得对，应是谨慎点的好。晶王后那处一有消息，我立即通知你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 92,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    }
